title: The First Ever Radio Hour 8/22/22
itunes:title: The First Ever Radio Hour 8/22/22
description:
This weeks radio hour is a mishmash of songs that have been floating around Jeremy's head. Hear music from Frank Black, Greet Death, Death Cab For Cutie, Mission of Burma, Rival Schools, That Dog, Pylon and more!

Subscribe to the PATREON and receive a brand new radio hour every Sunday! Thats two additional episodes a month AND you get them a day early! You'll also see a complete list of songs played on this episode.

Follow the show on Instagram and Twitter!
